  "Description": {
    "English": "A well-baked cookie, created in the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Nutrient Processor</span>.<br><br>What was once a thin sheet of vaguely-sweetend nutrient paste has been elevated with the addition of carefully-chosen ingredients.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">营养处理器</span>生产的上好饼干。<br><br>精挑细选的各类食材为原本略带甜味的营养糊带来了让人流连忘返的滋味。",
    "TencentChinese": "GoogleTranslated",
    "TraditionalChinese": "精心烘焙的餅乾，是在<span class=\"name name-technology\">營養處理器</span>中製成。<br><br>原本甜味不太明顯的營養糊薄片，在添加嚴選食材後，風味更上一層樓。"
  },
